1) Create a procedure P1 that inserts numbers from 1 to 10 into table t1 which has only one column named a of int type. Use while loop only.

	CREATE TABLE t1(a INT);

	DELIMITER //
	CREATE PROCEDURE P1()
	BEGIN
		DECLARE i int DEFAULT 1;
